item.description:
Our friends in Ireland (meetup group ...NEW AND NOT SO NEW IN DUBLIN.)..have invited us to join them for a Sunday brunch, coffee, friendship or just a walk around the little seacoast town of Howth, just outside of Dublin. This will be on our "free Sunday". So come join us as we meet with our new friends to share cultures, cheer and laughter!

Read on (from the website of NEW AND NOT SO NEW IN DUBLIN).... BTW , I would like to have some numbers ...but no real committment is needed here. Some of us, I know are going, others may not as may have other things to do. It's up to you, and it's your day! But you are welcome to come!


Come join us for some great food and coffee in K C Peaches, meet the members of Meet-up from Connecticut and New York who are in Dublin for the weekend and then head to Howth on the Dart for a Autumn walk.
item.name: Brunch and Walk in Howth 15th November
